NAME
    Mojolicious::Plugin::SimpleSlides - Create a presentation using
    Mojolicious

DESCRIPTION
    This module has been extracted from a talk gave at Chicago.pm. I have
    rushed it out before the talk, it has almost no tests or documentation.
    For the moment its use is at your own risk.

SEE ALSO
    Mojolicious, Mojolicious::Plugin::PPI

